Introduction
This Student Planner and Organization App is a web-based application designed to help students manage their schedules, keep track of assignments, and monitor their grades. The app is built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript and includes an imported calendar for easy schedule management.

Features
Calendar Integration: View and manage your schedule with an interactive calendar.
Task Management: Add, edit, and delete tasks and assignments.
Grade Tracking: Keep track of your grades and calculate GPA.
Responsive Design: The app is fully responsive and works on both desktop and mobile devices.
Technologies Used
HTML: Structure of the app
CSS: Styling and layout
JavaScript: Interactivity and functionality
External Libraries:
FullCalendar.js for calendar integration
Installation